merge subtitles with video:
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -i subs.srt -c copy -c:s mov_text output.mp4

extract subtitles from video:
ffmpeg -i output.mp4 -map 0:s:0 -c:s srt extracted_subtitles.srt
ffmpeg -i C:/Users/lukXmelo/Documents/GitHub/subSyncEditor/my-electron-app/videos/wot_burasque.mp4 -map 0:s:0 -c:s srt extracted_subtitles.srt
ffmpeg -i C:/Users/lukXmelo/Documents/GitHub/subSyncEditor/my-electron-app/videos/output.mp4 -map 0:s:0 -c:s srt extracted_subtitles.srt


